id: pm-sh4x
title: "UX: Telemetry shows 84 'No update flags provided' errors - improve guidance"
description: "Telemetry analysis shows 84 occurrences of 'No update flags provided' error. Users call pm update <ID> without specifying what to change. The error message should proactively suggest common flags (--status, --description, --body, --tags). Additionally 70 errors for 'Invalid --status value closed' - users try --status closed instead of pm close. And 56 errors for 'Item undefined not found' suggesting a caller passes no ID."
type: Issue
status: closed
